{"tid":1303922,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Now新聞台：特朗普減少批評香港修例爭議換重啟中美貿易談判","createTime":"2019-07-10T12:53:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-11T04:12:05.000Z","uid":57677,"like":9,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"cd19df89837661187b269ac105464b42a58676a6","tid":1303922,"uid":57677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T12:53:28.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】英國傳媒報道，美國總統特朗普向國家主席習近平承諾，減少批評香港修訂逃犯條例爭議，換取重啟中美貿易談判，在北京，外交部重申，外國無權干預中國內政。<br />\n<br />\n國家主席習近平上月在大阪二十國集團峰會期間，跟美國總統特朗普舉行會談，英國《金融時報》引述消息報道，特朗普為了重啟中美貿易談判，承諾華府在香港修例爭議上會減少批評北京。<br />\n<br />\n消息又指，特朗普在會面前的電話對話，亦有向習近平作出類似的承諾，美國白宮未有回應報道的內容。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=354925\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D354925&d=q18Y%2F9yBacX5GGPSgvrSC%2FkXgXr6FxeO6pMo8RORPdo%3D&h=43a0932d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D354925&h=2d3f8ea6\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=354925</a>"},{"pid":"8ac2125fb75b5c896a50620647091431241a1d7d","tid":1303922,"uid":54303,"like":39,"dislike":0,"score":39,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T12:54:32.000Z","msg":"另一方面，侵侵會派親信同香港泛民接觸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7072c5c6beb212ffb55fc310ec01564f35515ae7","tid":1303922,"uid":63909,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T12:56:16.000Z","msg":"調轉仲似啲<br />\n如果唔似一早3讀啦"},{"pid":"e9bcecfe45daf4519c962e892d91854d49954f18","tid":1303922,"uid":63909,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7072c5c6beb212ffb55fc310ec01564f35515ae7","tid":1303922,"uid":63909,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T12:56:16.000Z","msg":"調轉仲似啲<br />\n如果唔似一早3讀啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T12:56:41.000Z","msg":"*唔係"},{"pid":"f980059af80704b84bc1bb410819687b0ada64c5","tid":1303922,"uid":132287,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8